articles.title: Marvin Harrison leads No. 3 Ohio State past No. 7 Penn State - ESPN
articles.description: All-American Marvin Harrison made all the difference for No. 3 Ohio State in a pivotal Big Ten matchup, making 11 catches for 162 yards and a late touchdown as the Buckeyes beat No. 7 Penn State 20-12 on Saturday in Columbus, Ohio.
articles.content:
